-- Icahn has bought up to 50 mln Yahoo shares: report
-- 
-- Tue May 13, 2008 5:06pm EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2008/05/13/us-yahoo-icahn-shares-idUSGOR37578820080513

 

 NEW YORK  (Reuters) - Carl Icahn has bought as many as 50 million Yahoo ( YHOO.O ) shares, and is leading towards starting a proxy fight, according to a report on the Wall Street Journal's Web site. 

